 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf6be63c71bc9992a6b4ab4b8fadb366a59f5ce","tid":235002,"uid":13105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T17:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>決絕 千奇唔好話咩仲鍾意但因為乜啲原因一齊唔到 好心就直接話已經唔鍾意 就算係假<br />\n最仆街係一邊自稱決絕 一邊話其實仲鍾意你<br />\n好心唔好不停俾假希望人啦<br />\n拖拖拉拉嗰啲都好黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係仲鐘意，但轉頭就話分手，消失曬咁，我寧願另一伴侶會心軟，因為仲好愛佢會比多次機會我都好"},{"pid":"946d045cd4a215efa3894a18e92ea8d3660570aa","tid":235002,"uid":28478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T18:00:39.000Z","msg":"我男朋友對我幾時都係咁決絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分一次手 要用幾日去求佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4095066cf8c569d86f426e5edb543987a186ef42","tid":235002,"uid":114722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T18:13:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳩硬心軟</blockquote><br />\n同意"},{"pid":"8927bf1d527dee48f4ecc0bcc36cfa989071bcb4","tid":235002,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T18:20:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22a0c88285d8b33926735598cebe5114fc4156e9","tid":235002,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T18:21:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58a896f3454f9b47379f9714ada9729f553b76fd","tid":235002,"uid":104164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T18:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我男朋友對我幾時都係咁決絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分一次手 要用幾日去求佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點求？ 我而家都係咁 好想放棄但又唔甘心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92b91f12107afeedf96b8a87d700f9c257ff436","tid":235002,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:06:43.000Z","msg":"我係決絕個種人 所以傷過我第一個男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f66c6c02e504f05d41bcc140df734377c35ea50","tid":235002,"uid":23103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:08:04.000Z","msg":"決絕"},{"pid":"69c1fc0a6436819f1f318c80ea1141b728f47679","tid":235002,"uid":13105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我男朋友對我幾時都係咁決絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分一次手 要用幾日去求佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我女朋友對我決絕，有咩建議比下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf86127a02934a36bfd4eb44b1d3c75e90d55de","tid":235002,"uid":13105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:17:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係決絕個種人 所以傷過我第一個男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打，決絕有好有唔好既，但對我黎講對方咁努力挽回點解唔可以比下機會，又唔係每樣野都要去到咁盡既，唉"},{"pid":"047cdc56c85c52fe6cf06e9bf0a21cd2f0126c5d","tid":235002,"uid":13105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:19:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>決絕 千奇唔好話咩仲鍾意但因為乜啲原因一齊唔到 好心就直接話已經唔鍾意 就算係假<br />\n最仆街係一邊自稱決絕 一邊話其實仲鍾意你<br />\n好心唔好不停俾假希望人啦<br />\n拖拖拉拉嗰啲都好黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係仲鐘意，但轉頭就話分手，消失曬咁，我寧願另一伴侶會心軟，因為仲好愛佢會比多次機會我都好</blockquote><br />\n心軟只會兩個都辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n心軟對我黎講係希望對方比次機會佢去珍惜，都唔好去一刀切就咁放棄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c04a7cb320d4d365c2c568c509b7dd1862fa560","tid":235002,"uid":79999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:32:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>決絕 千奇唔好話咩仲鍾意但因為乜啲原因一齊唔到 好心就直接話已經唔鍾意 就算係假<br />\n最仆街係一邊自稱決絕 一邊話其實仲鍾意你<br />\n好心唔好不停俾假希望人啦<br />\n拖拖拉拉嗰啲都好黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係仲鐘意，但轉頭就話分手，消失曬咁，我寧願另一伴侶會心軟，因為仲好愛佢會比多次機會我都好</blockquote><br />\n心軟只會兩個都辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n心軟對我黎講係希望對方比次機會佢去珍惜，都唔好去一刀切就咁放棄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最近同女朋友分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然我仲鐘意佢，佢亦係一個好女仔，但最近因為某些原因令到自己冇晒信心未來會同佢走落去，又唔想拖佢。所以都做左一個決絕既衰人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我呢一刻個心真係好痛.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ddcea7a36a171ad950dc2de161cdead79b80b28","tid":235002,"uid":105955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:35:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>決絕 千奇唔好話咩仲鍾意但因為乜啲原因一齊唔到 好心就直接話已經唔鍾意 就算係假<br />\n最仆街係一邊自稱決絕 一邊話其實仲鍾意你<br />\n好心唔好不停俾假希望人啦<br />\n拖拖拉拉嗰啲都好黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係仲鐘意，但轉頭就話分手，消失曬咁，我寧願另一伴侶會心軟，因為仲好愛佢會比多次機會我都好</blockquote><br />\n心軟只會兩個都辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n心軟對我黎講係希望對方比次機會佢去珍惜，都唔好去一刀切就咁放棄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比多次機會咪都係唔珍惜 我就寧願決絕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30801700955dd50621b1f9ac3e4ef3c38abd02c1","tid":235002,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T19:39:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>決絕 千奇唔好話咩仲鍾意但因為乜啲原因一齊唔到 好心就直接話已經唔鍾意 就算係假<br />\n最仆街係一邊自稱決絕 一邊話其實仲鍾意你<br />\n好心唔好不停俾假希望人啦<br />\n拖拖拉拉嗰啲都好黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係仲鐘意，但轉頭就話分手，消失曬咁，我寧願另一伴侶會心軟，因為仲好愛佢會比多次機會我都好</blockquote><br />\n心軟只會兩個都辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n心軟對我黎講係希望對方比次機會佢去珍惜，都唔好去一刀切就咁放棄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比多次機會咪都係唔珍惜 我就寧願決絕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger"},{"pid":"faaa4bad0a74608e83a766682b303d61d9bb6658","tid":235002,"uid":3935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T21:23:45.000Z","msg":"對我心軟對其他人決絕<br />\n<br />\n利申, 佢真係個咁既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a83b6a841ed202a2fed32291b80bc0dc57b918","tid":235002,"uid":13105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T21:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>決絕 千奇唔好話咩仲鍾意但因為乜啲原因一齊唔到 好心就直接話已經唔鍾意 就算係假<br />\n最仆街係一邊自稱決絕 一邊話其實仲鍾意你<br />\n好心唔好不停俾假希望人啦<br />\n拖拖拉拉嗰啲都好黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係仲鐘意，但轉頭就話分手，消失曬咁，